biotools.summary: An open source GUI software consisting of two modules: Topology Enrichment Analysis frameworK  and Query Structure Enrichment Analysis. TEAK is used to find biologically activated KEGG subpathways given molecular profiling data whereas QSEA is used to perform hierarchical querying of the KEGG pathways.
